init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world is in your hands.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The game is set in a world where Mana is the source of all power.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Mana is gained by playing cards.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The game is played in turns.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Each turn is divided into two phases: the draw phase and the action phase.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The action phase is where the player can play cards.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The card is then placed in front of the player.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The player can then take the Mana from that source well.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The game ends when the last card is drawn from the stack.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The player with the most Mana wins.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The game was designed by James Ernest and Patrick Rothfuss.

actions.name: text-insert
